Package: ParametricSurvFit
Type: Package
Title: Parametric Survival Model Fitting and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Gosuke", "Homma",
      email = "my.name.is.gosuke@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A comprehensive package for fitting multiple parametric survival 
    distributions to clinical trial data. Supports exponential, Weibull, 
    log-normal, log-logistic, Gompertz, generalized gamma, and gamma 
    distributions. Provides formatted output tables and stratified analysis 
    capabilities for ADaM datasets commonly used in pharmaceutical research.
